ware ($100 200)"},"id":"8abeacfc-3a5b-47ff-8ad8-7a8ba53c8062","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Most small retails, who do not sell to other vendors, can get by with a simple <a href=\"https://www.toptenreviews.com/business/payment-processing/best-pos-systems/\">barcode program</a>. If you want to design your own labels and only want to work with a few codes, programs like B Coder or UPC Tools will satisfy your needs. They are simple to use and copy into other programs easily. If you want one program that generates barcodes and creates labels, software like IDAutomation and My Tattoo ID are a good fit. These programs include a variety of barcode fonts and have a label creator in the same program."]},"id":"49620a40-51f7-473e-8df4-27e24c1a6f1b","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Marketing ($80 90)"},"id":"41c7590d-c8c3-4759-b2ac-b423e5ae6ce6","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Nearly all retailers make use of flyers, coupons, business cards, brochures and other printed marketing materials. Programs like Art Explosion Publisher Pro, PagePlus and Print Shop Pro Publisher can create printable items with company logos and images easily. These programs can also be used to create newsletters, stationary, CD labels, simple web pages, greeting cards and much more."]},"id":"e6884a4d-e0bb-4033-af9f-a8c7511c628f","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Accounting Software ($200 300)"},"id":"f7b085eb-272c-4c77-bd3c-821ef81a8305","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Keeping the books is easier with a good accounting program like Peachtree, MYOB or Quickbooks. These programs can manage everything from accounts receivable to payroll to invoicing. If you purchase the Quickbooks POS software the Quickbooks accounting program is 100% compatible.","At TopTenREVIEWS We Do the Research So You Don t Have To. "," "]},"id":"b44352e6-d883-4bd9-a745-aae1a75491b0","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"article_page_663","url":"/the-perfect-software-collection-for-small-retails","auth